{"tid":1764331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"94%人幫襯黃店 受訪者：良知最重要","createTime":"2019-12-01T04:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T06:40:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1102c190ba4f503dd6c44abf412cde3e3df27116","tid":1764331,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191201/TGXKVI4Z5EIHBTB2TAILPBDBDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191201%2FTGXKVI4Z5EIHBTB2TAILPBDBDE%2F&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=8d63ad75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191201%2FTGXKVI4Z5EIHBTB2TAILPBDBDE%2F&h=bd83d117\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191201/TGXKVI4Z5EIHBTB2TAILPBDBDE/</a><br />\n<br />\n94%人幫襯黃店 受訪者：良知最重要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191201/large/1575130406_9f3b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575130406_9f3b.gif&h=964f47e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n退休人士劉先生<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】除了數之不盡的示威、遊行外，港人亦將抗爭融入生活，以和理非手段支援運動和表達訴求。問卷查詢了運動支持者在遊行和集會以外，參與其他行動的情況，當中絕大部份人有幫襯黃店（94％）及拒絕幫襯撐警、撐政府的藍店（89.6％）。受訪者亦高度參與「捐助支援示威者、被捕者的基金」（71.6％）、「罷搭港鐵」（70.1％）和「派發文宣、貼連儂牆」（66.7％）等和理非抗爭行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警屢改傷者數字 難解打死人疑團<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191201/large/1575130405_6ae3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575130405_6ae3.gif&h=c2650f3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191201/large/1575130405_6684.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575130405_6684.gif&h=10753d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191201/large/1575130406_9dc0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575130406_9dc0.gif&h=f7eb2219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔好食都照去」<br />\n<br />\n網民構想在運動中建立「黃色經濟圈」，呼籲港人努力幫襯支持示威者的商戶、餐廳。問卷查詢了黃店被「懲罰」的嚴重程度，多達35.3％運動支持者表示，一星期內光顧撐示威者餐廳多達五次以上，幫襯了三至四次的受訪者亦共有34.4％，顯示不少人都刻意將自己的消費力投放到同路人之中。<br />\n<br />\n退休人士劉先生表示，近日出外用膳的習慣已經改變，不再以食物質素為首要考慮，「係憑住兩個字──良知，良知凌駕於一切&hellip;&hellip;好老實講，龍門冰室啲嘢唔好食，但我都會照去食。冇咗良知，更好食嘅嘢你都食唔出個味道」。吳先生每星期亦光顧最少五次撐示威者餐廳，會參考手機應用程式，查證食肆的立場，「希望逐步形成生活嘅習慣，去支持撐民主嘅店舖」。"},{"pid":"fb674de2c6cd9848c3c795cf41dd4ceb32750af4","tid":1764331,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72c87aaeafcb1fc634a91cb14e515ee76deeb59","tid":1764331,"uid":283539,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"唔係難食到嘔都會食"},{"pid":"e5136192170599cbde03afc0ca9c5110cde35655","tid":1764331,"uid":8219,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"龍門d 野都算唔好食的話佢應該未食過真係難食既黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都會撐黃色經濟"},{"pid":"f9b53cee2ffd4fcaf8186d8919540c777ed52c3c","tid":1764331,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5136192170599cbde03afc0ca9c5110cde35655","tid":1764331,"uid":8219,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"龍門d 野都算唔好食的話佢應該未食過真係難食既黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都會撐黃色經濟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"load左一陣唔明你講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f780e69701d732fea05ed0166310b741b63094a","tid":1764331,"uid":35031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5136192170599cbde03afc0ca9c5110cde35655","tid":1764331,"uid":8219,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"龍門d 野都算唔好食的話佢應該未食過真係難食既黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都會撐黃色經濟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:05:25.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n好食一定未到<br />\n但一定唔係難食囉<br />\n份量一定夠<br />\n價錢都公道<br />\n連鎖快餐店以上出名餐廳以下咁"},{"pid":"cbad61ff592f78f168b1a9d584622d5efaa80086","tid":1764331,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5136192170599cbde03afc0ca9c5110cde35655","tid":1764331,"uid":8219,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"龍門d 野都算唔好食的話佢應該未食過真係難食既黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都會撐黃色經濟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"都係一般茶記質素啦冇話好唔好食"},{"pid":"8439622444810eee1a8580799fbc4ebadf3541f0","tid":1764331,"uid":1348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:06:06.000Z","msg":"70%罷搭港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7683fcc30d7aada9903b71d05c673fc237ec787d","tid":1764331,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"良知"},{"pid":"45548ea0349e2f325c1fdd557e0167a51b290f43","tid":1764331,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5136192170599cbde03afc0ca9c5110cde35655","tid":1764331,"uid":8219,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"龍門d 野都算唔好食的話佢應該未食過真係難食既黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我都會撐黃色經濟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T05:06:58.000Z","msg":"紅磡龍門我覺得好食wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf281569f584d42